I feel in the war against Bots, we will be sacrificing humans. I've already had to give up going to a popular site since they have too strict a captcha (blaming Hcaptcha specifically here). Eventually we will have to live in a society where Bots and Humans live together. When you start talking about banning "non-humans" from the internet, it will inevitably devolve into ableism as well.</div>
