		<div id="comment_body_64607045"><p>It's not terms of service, it's just how copyright works. If you aren't given explicit permission, you have no right to make an retain a copy nor use it to create derivative works.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64607045">

